  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914970/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.poster.avif?t=1758745154\" width=736 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914970/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.webm?t=1758745154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914970/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.mp4?t=1758745154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914970/extras/e3f9369e810da10828c432e7c694964a.avif?t=1758745154\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>Robo Pose is a difficult game about Robot that needs to strike the right Pose in order to overcome procedurally generated obstacles.<br>Games core mechanics are inspired by idea of characters from cartoons that leave their body outlines when they go through the wall, but here you need to fit in those outlines in order to overcome failure.<br>Can you help Robo escape?<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Coordinate Robots moving body parts<br></li><li> Rage inducing gameplay<br></li><li> Failure<br></li><li> Repeat<br></li><li> Hone Skills<br></li><li> Escape<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914970/extras/30d4611a30563600fa60c0926699c1de.avif?t=1758745154\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Note: This Is My First Game. Hope You Like It.</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914970/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.poster.avif?t=1758745154\" width=736 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914970/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.webm?t=1758745154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914970/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.mp4?t=1758745154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914970/extras/e3f9369e810da10828c432e7c694964a.avif?t=1758745154\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>Robo Pose is a difficult game about Robot that needs to strike the right Pose in order to overcome procedurally generated obstacles.<br>Games core mechanics are inspired by idea of characters from cartoons that leave their body outlines when they go through the wall, but here you need to fit in those outlines in order to overcome failure.<br>Can you help Robo escape?<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Coordinate Robots moving body parts<br></li><li> Rage inducing gameplay<br></li><li> Failure<br></li><li> Repeat<br></li><li> Hone Skills<br></li><li> Escape<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914970/extras/30d4611a30563600fa60c0926699c1de.avif?t=1758745154\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Note: This Is My First Game. Hope You Like It.</h2>",
